Nouns also introduced an identity, community, government and treasury approach that is brining NFTs to a next level. NounRalph is a collection of 99 NFTs on the Ethereum / Polygon blockchain. They are based on the CryptoRalph art, age groups and attributes. Each NounRalph has a unique set attributes showing details of real Ralph's life (just like CryptoRalph).
